ildcats Football Schedule|url=https://fbschedules.com/ncaa-2019/team/kentucky|publisher=FB Schedules|accessdate=January 15, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Personnel==\n===Coaching staff===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Kentucky Wildcats|Name|Position}}\n|-\n| [[Mark Stoops]] || Head Coach \n|-\n| \u2013 |[[Eddie Gran]]   || Offensive Coordinator/Associate Head Coach, RB Coach\n|-\n| \u2013 |Brad White   || Defensive Coordinator/Linebackers Coach\n|-\n| \u2013 | [[Vince Marrow]] || Tight Ends Coach/Recruiting Coordinator \n|-\n| \u2013 |[[Steve Clinkscale]]|| Secondary Coach\n|-\n| \u2013 | Michael Smith   || Wide Receivers Coach \t\n|-\n| \u2013 |  Darin Hinshaw|| Co-Offensive Coordinator, Quarterbacks Coach\n|-\n| \u2013 |[[John Schlarman]]  || Offensive Line Coach\n|-\n| \u2013 | [[Derrick LeBlanc]]|| Defensive Line Coach\n|-\n| \u2013 |Dean Hood || LB Coach/Special Teams Coordinator\n|}\n\n==Game summaries==\n===Toledo===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=Rockets\n|R1=7 |R2=7 |R3=3 |R4=7\n|Home='''Wildcats'''\n|H1=0 |H2=14|H3=10|H4=14\n}}\n{{see also|2019 Toledo Rockets football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Kentucky Wildcats|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n|colspan=3|''First meeting''\n|}\n\n===Eastern Michigan===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=Eagles\n|R1=0 |R2=3 |R3=7 |R4=7\n|Home='''Wildcats'''\n|H1=14 |H2=3 |H3=7 |H4=14\n}}\n{{see also|2019 Eastern Michigan Eagles football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Kentucky Wildcats|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n|1\u20130\n|Sept. 30, [[2017 Kentucky Wildcats football team|2017]]\n|'''W''', 24\u201320\n|}\n\n===Florida===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road='''No. 9 Gators'''\n|R1=7 |R2=0 |R3=3 |R4=19\n|Home=Wildcats\n|H1=0 |H2=14|H3=7 |H4=0\n}}\n{{see also|2019 Florida Gators football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Kentucky Wildcats|Overall record|Last ten meetings|Last